I've Port Forwarded Correctly i believe because when i check my port it says OPEN. I've also port forwarded with Utorrent and after Utorrent it worked once but i wanted to change Sources so after i did that it stopped working. I don't know what else to say, If you can help PLEASE DO SO i will return the favor. If you need more info PLEASE ask and i also Have Team Viewer! Thanks!
